    "gp_bands": {
      "name": "Sales Rep (GP Incremental Bands)",
      "description": "For Sales Reps (Daniel, Nic). Five-band structure: true no-commission floor at $100k, soft start from $100-200k, ramps through $200-300k so $300k matches old 3.5% flat, accelerates past $400k. Band output is super-INCLUSIVE. 1% production commission on Event GP (also super-inclusive). Quarterly true-ups net against a running balance that carries forward (no clawback from base).",
