    "hybrid_gp": {
      "name": "Sales-Producer Hybrid (GP Sales + Production)",
      "description": "For Evie & Evie 2.0. Five-band monotonic structure with $50k no-commission floor (half the Sales Rep floor). Match at $150k (old 3.5%+super ~$5,880), clear win at $200k (~$12,000 vs old+super $7,840 = +$4,160), and rates continue climbing above $200k at 13% — 2 points under Daniel's 15% top so Evie's stretch stays meaningful without out-paying Sales Rep stretch per dollar. 1% production commission on Event GP drives the bulk of Evie's earnings. Band output is super-INCLUSIVE.",
